{"tid":871372,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《神經俠侶》續集因「佔中」而被腰斬","createTime":"2018-10-22T01:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T10:24:54.000Z","uid":134071,"like":136,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"64960bafb6aa518f64d0ee15ff7cd9e078a05934","tid":871372,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:16:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/groups/803879953032830/permalink/1933672310053583/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F803879953032830%2Fpermalink%2F1933672310053583%2F&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5793be6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/groups/803879953032830/permalink/1933672310053583/</a><br />\n<br />\nPeter Chun-ngai Kong 分享了 1 則帖子。<br />\n9 小時<br />\n<br />\n《神經俠侶》座談會精華<br />\n<br />\n《神經俠侶》導演阮世生跟編劇羅耀輝剛出席灣仔座談會。阮世生滲露了不少有趣內幕，更爆出《神經俠侶》續集為何因雨傘運動而胎死腹中：<br />\n<br />\n1）《神經俠侶》故事原定由陳奕迅和容祖兒演武功俠侶， 但陳奕迅唔識功夫， 要改故事，加上後沙士環境影響，攪攪下變左差佬行必既故事。選擇故事地區時， 最後選灣仔， 因為灣仔代表到香港現象。（羅耀輝指出此片是有關香港人在困境如何自強的故事。）<br />\n<br />\n2） 吳鎮字的角色，原本為《金雞2》而寫， 但遭陳可辛否決，故起用在此片中。容祖兒心態接近她本身個性。<br />\n<br />\n3）惠英紅只拍了兩天。態度很專業。<br />\n<br />\n4）好多場面都係在街頭偷拍。最後灣仔警察局出禁令， 禁止在1200 至1400 拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n5）市道較差時，較易偷拍， 陀地也沒有騷擾。而家， 好難再偷拍了。<br />\n<br />\n6）對演員而言， 自已演出唔係最難， 跟對手合作先係最難。陳奕迅和容祖兒係大部分時間跟演技派錄葉同場演出， 會比較容易。吳鎮宇在很多場面跟內地新人女演員同場演出， 有時會較辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n7）吳鎮宇跟惠英紅做某場對手戲，吳鎮宇在每個takes都利用唔同演法，惠英紅有時也感到辛苦。阮世生叫惠英紅做好自己本分便行， 不必因吳鎮宇而改變。最後靠剪接令場面可以連貫起來。（羅耀輝：吳鎮宇跟足劇本80%對白。）<br />\n<br />\n8） 吳鎮字跑步好fit，陳奕迅有d困難。片尾追捕鏡頭拍左3日。全片拍了30多天。<br />\n<br />\n9）曾諗住改片名，但因諗唔到更好片名便作罷。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>10）阮世生原本已在籌備拍攝《神經俠侶》續集，已經構思好故事， 陳奕迅和容祖兒都同意演出。在續集中，陳奕迅原定會跟內地女演員有愛情線， 因為當時拍電影，一定要加中國元素。<br />\n<br />\n11）但後來，因雨傘運動改變了對警察的想法， 阮世生決定取消拍攝《神經俠侶》續集。</strong><br />\n<br />\n12） 如果而家拍灣仔警察，一定要涉及示威先合符現實， 但拍出來又恐怕太敏感。<br />\n<br />\n13）阮世生指出「呼應」在電影架構中必須存在。有人喜歡經常即興地度橋和拍攝， 但他就喜歡嚴謹一點。<br />\n<br />\n14）阮世生指他在過去長時間寫普通話對白， 已唔接香港地氣。 如果要再拍有香港本土味的電影， 便要花兩年認識香港生活。<br />\n<br />\n15） 阮世生指他經常讀報紙， 將有意思的事情keep在folders中。他指出創作要靠留意生活， 留意社會。他在TVB工作和拍電影時，也要經常做資料搜集，訪問不同人士。要拍香港本土電影， 最重要的一環，就是「資料搜集」。"},{"pid":"4a123e4fa05210f2736b7c8c9cc0e63fafbaf715","tid":871372,"uid":126044,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>11）但後來，因雨傘運動改變了對警察的想法， 阮世生決定取消拍攝《神經俠侶》續集<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n個判斷冇錯<br />\n呢個時候再拍落去<br />\n就算本意唔係撐警都一定俾人屌爆"},{"pid":"034a40bc0beaf10c8cfe4f05c41fbf810e7ddc69","tid":871372,"uid":77092,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:36:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e93f980fae526923e536f4a3f8ec4b3656ee78ff","tid":871372,"uid":28181,"like":97,"dislike":3,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:40:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但後來，因雨傘運動改變了對警察的想法， 阮世生決定取消拍攝《神經俠侶》續集。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3769509726aaf744d4bdbaff158845861000f6","tid":871372,"uid":135132,"like":4,"dislike":20,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"我記錯神經俠侶咗係古天樂吳君如套古裝片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d330d66ed21b522255326ecc59feff54f5eebdc4","tid":871372,"uid":149122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c3769509726aaf744d4bdbaff158845861000f6","tid":871372,"uid":135132,"like":4,"dislike":20,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"我記錯神經俠侶咗係古天樂吳君如套古裝片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"神奇俠侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febaee29f867bca6240af2b0c29ae69863ee100b","tid":871372,"uid":134071,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"d330d66ed21b522255326ecc59feff54f5eebdc4","tid":871372,"uid":149122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c3769509726aaf744d4bdbaff158845861000f6","tid":871372,"uid":135132,"like":4,"dislike":20,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"我記錯神經俠侶咗係古天樂吳君如套古裝片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"神奇俠侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:49:17.000Z","msg":"呢套好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1c516d76a7a472f9860c7b88b01cbc40d0dfb1","tid":871372,"uid":77788,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5b14ede50b5ce50df9df10a018f991cc73d0794","tid":871372,"uid":61300,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:32:49.000Z","msg":"吳鎮字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92ce98fec816f5863434302f5a4fd5626ef05a8","tid":871372,"uid":29447,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:40:09.000Z","msg":"睇戲名覺得好膠<br />\n但呢套小品真係幾好睇"},{"pid":"b1da2e75e6c386c7fd3e301d1c45294e71a6c804","tid":871372,"uid":37358,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:02:35.000Z","msg":"呢套好睇到仆街<br />\n仲記得智叔一開頭講果句好頭好尾"},{"pid":"c3704f5c261918401d2693dc84a3f23e5786f06e","tid":871372,"uid":180173,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:14:07.000Z","msg":"神戲，好鐘意，乜都有d，悲情得離臨尾又有番希望，勵志"},{"pid":"1973bb616cb682e7f1d01f494eb9e0b0f7a57f83","tid":871372,"uid":180173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a92ce98fec816f5863434302f5a4fd5626ef05a8","tid":871372,"uid":29447,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:40:09.000Z","msg":"睇戲名覺得好膠<br />\n但呢套小品真係幾好睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:14:54.000Z","msg":"好多on9仔話個戲名on9就無睇lu"},{"pid":"c6eed5d264e3833cb5b09f23681827a8ddf93215","tid":871372,"uid":180173,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"64960bafb6aa518f64d0ee15ff7cd9e078a05934","tid":871372,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:16:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/groups/803879953032830/permalink/1933672310053583/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F803879953032830%2Fpermalink%2F1933672310053583%2F&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5793be6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/groups/803879953032830/permalink/1933672310053583/</a><br />\n<br />\nPeter Chun-ngai Kong 分享了 1 則帖子。<br />\n9 小時<br />\n<br />\n《神經俠侶》座談會精華<br />\n<br />\n《神經俠侶》導演阮世生跟編劇羅耀輝剛出席灣仔座談會。阮世生滲露了不少有趣內幕，更爆出《神經俠侶》續集為何因雨傘運動而胎死腹中：<br />\n<br />\n1）《神經俠侶》故事原定由陳奕迅和容祖兒演武功俠侶， 但陳奕迅唔識功夫， 要改故事，加上後沙士環境影響，攪攪下變左差佬行必既故事。選擇故事地區時， 最後選灣仔， 因為灣仔代表到香港現象。（羅耀輝指出此片是有關香港人在困境如何自強的故事。）<br />\n<br />\n2） 吳鎮字的角色，原本為《金雞2》而寫， 但遭陳可辛否決，故起用在此片中。容祖兒心態接近她本身個性。<br />\n<br />\n3）惠英紅只拍了兩天。態度很專業。<br />\n<br />\n4）好多場面都係在街頭偷拍。最後灣仔警察局出禁令， 禁止在1200 至1400 拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n5）市道較差時，較易偷拍， 陀地也沒有騷擾。而家， 好難再偷拍了。<br />\n<br />\n6）對演員而言， 自已演出唔係最難， 跟對手合作先係最難。陳奕迅和容祖兒係大部分時間跟演技派錄葉同場演出， 會比較容易。吳鎮宇在很多場面跟內地新人女演員同場演出， 有時會較辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n7）吳鎮宇跟惠英紅做某場對手戲，吳鎮宇在每個takes都利用唔同演法，惠英紅有時也感到辛苦。阮世生叫惠英紅做好自己本分便行， 不必因吳鎮宇而改變。最後靠剪接令場面可以連貫起來。（羅耀輝：吳鎮宇跟足劇本80%對白。）<br />\n<br />\n8） 吳鎮字跑步好fit，陳奕迅有d困難。片尾追捕鏡頭拍左3日。全片拍了30多天。<br />\n<br />\n9）曾諗住改片名，但因諗唔到更好片名便作罷。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>10）阮世生原本已在籌備拍攝《神經俠侶》續集，已經構思好故事， 陳奕迅和容祖兒都同意演出。在續集中，陳奕迅原定會跟內地女演員有愛情線， 因為當時拍電影，一定要加中國元素。<br />\n<br />\n11）但後來，因雨傘運動改變了對警察的想法， 阮世生決定取消拍攝《神經俠侶》續集。</strong><br />\n<br />\n12） 如果而家拍灣仔警察，一定要涉及示威先合符現實， 但拍出來又恐怕太敏感。<br />\n<br />\n13）阮世生指出「呼應」在電影架構中必須存在。有人喜歡經常即興地度橋和拍攝， 但他就喜歡嚴謹一點。<br />\n<br />\n14）阮世生指他在過去長時間寫普通話對白， 已唔接香港地氣。 如果要再拍有香港本土味的電影， 便要花兩年認識香港生活。<br />\n<br />\n15） 阮世生指他經常讀報紙， 將有意思的事情keep在folders中。他指出創作要靠留意生活， 留意社會。他在TVB工作和拍電影時，也要經常做資料搜集，訪問不同人士。要拍香港本土電影， 最重要的一環，就是「資料搜集」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:16:12.000Z","msg":"14) 好撚認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739fbf979cada74c86242341b52a1e02be790214","tid":871372,"uid":29447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3704f5c261918401d2693dc84a3f23e5786f06e","tid":871372,"uid":180173,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:14:07.000Z","msg":"神戲，好鐘意，乜都有d，悲情得離臨尾又有番希望，勵志"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:18:10.000Z","msg":"出黎做野之後滑哂啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe719dbd680bafc98ab618cb2810721a577a6fee","tid":871372,"uid":9887,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1973bb616cb682e7f1d01f494eb9e0b0f7a57f83","tid":871372,"uid":180173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a92ce98fec816f5863434302f5a4fd5626ef05a8","tid":871372,"uid":29447,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:40:09.000Z","msg":"睇戲名覺得好膠<br />\n但呢套小品真係幾好睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:14:54.000Z","msg":"好多on9仔話個戲名on9就無睇lu"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"香港人睇戲有時係咁戇鳩<br />\n因為個名戇鳩而唔睇<br />\n因為有周潤發所以擺明戇鳩戲都去睇"},{"pid":"39db5b1ff606e7676979079fb7fbe9b445911940","tid":871372,"uid":21961,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"fe719dbd680bafc98ab618cb2810721a577a6fee","tid":871372,"uid":9887,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1973bb616cb682e7f1d01f494eb9e0b0f7a57f83","tid":871372,"uid":180173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a92ce98fec816f5863434302f5a4fd5626ef05a8","tid":871372,"uid":29447,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:40:09.000Z","msg":"睇戲名覺得好膠<br />\n但呢套小品真係幾好睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:14:54.000Z","msg":"好多on9仔話個戲名on9就無睇lu"},"citedBy":2,"replyT